{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"94f425ee59","title":"克敌制胜的有利条件叫","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ad96569995","index":0,"year":1930,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"94f425ee59"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji5","name":"毛泽东全集第5卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji5.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0d0e7923cb","type":"paragraph","text":"克敌制胜的有利条件叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"94f425ee59"},{"id":"1febe403c7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1930年12月）第一，我们军民一致，人民积极援助红军，这是最重要条件。第二，我们可以主动选择有利阵地，设下陷研，把敌人关在里面打。第三，我们可以集中优势兵力，歼灭敌人一部分，一口一口地把敌人吃掉。第四，我们可以察明敌军行动，摸清敌人行动规律，从而发现敌人的薄弱部分，拆弱的打。第五，我们可以把敌人拖得精疲力尽，然后再打。第六，我们可以造成敌人的过失，乘政之原，加以打击。[1]1930年12月下旬，毛泽东在小布主持召开苏区军民开敌普师大会","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"94f425ee59"}],"page":{"id":"fd8f51da18","publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"94f425ee59","start":240,"end":240}}}},"__N_SSG":true}